== My Video won't play, its a avi!? ==

mPlayer uses use flags to enable and disable support for various codecs. If a particular type of file wont play in mplayer, firstly check which use flags it was emerged with and then update the use flags to support for the format your trying to play and recompile.

== Disable Screensaver while playing a video ==
Should work for any freedesktop-compliant environment (like KDE).

{{File|~/.mplayer/config||<pre>
heartbeat-cmd="qdbus org.freedesktop.ScreenSaver /ScreenSaver SimulateUserActivity"
</pre>}}

